NK016(ma)017:0: 'o bran drag dmar gyi sgrub thabs dbang chog dang bcas pa bzhugs so //
NK016(ma)017:2: chos nyid zhi las g.yo med kyang //
NK016(ma)017:3: gdug gtum dregs pa'i gnyen po ru //
NK016(ma)017:4: cher khros dbang drag lhag pa'i lhar //
NK016(ma)017:5: btud nas sgrub thabs mdo tsam bshad //
NK016(ma)017:6: 'dir drag dmar 'o bran lugs su grags pa'i sgrub
NK016(ma)017:7: thabs dang 'brel bar dbang bskur ba la gsum ste
NK016(ma)017:8: / sbyor ba yo byad kyi shoms /
NK016(ma)017:9: dngos gzhi sgrub pa'i thabs dang /
NK016(ma)017:11: dang po yo byad bsham pa ni /
NK016(ma)017:12: stegs bu'i khar man+dala sgo rdzogs spyi mthun gyi lte
NK016(ma)017:13: bar chos 'byung zla gam gsum ldan rtsibs brgyad thod
NK016(ma)017:14: ras bskor ba rdul tshon gyis bris pa'am ras bris
NK016(ma)017:15: bkram / de'i dbus su many+dzi la bum pa bcud ldan gyi khar thod pa bdud rtsis gang ba /
NK016(ma)017:16: me long la sin+d+hu ras chos 'byung dang sngags bris pas bkab /
NK016(ma)017:17: steng nas dar dmar pos gur phub /
NK016(ma)017:18: dkyil 'khor gyi shar du rdo rje /
NK016(ma)017:19: lhor thod pa bdud rtsi can /
NK016(ma)017:22: dbus sam shar du rdo rje dang lcags sdig gi gzugs rnams bzhag /
NK016(ma)017:23: mdun du sman raka gtor gsum dang /
NK016(ma)017:26: mig dar me tog sogs nyer mkho'i yo byad thams cad tshogs par bsham mo //
NK016(ma)017:28: sngon 'gro ni bgegs bskrad mtshams bcad /
NK016(ma)017:29: hoh sku gsum lha tshogs nam mkha' khyab pa la //
NK016(ma)017:30: phyag 'tshal gus mchod sdig bshags yi rang 'bul //
NK016(ma)017:31: ka dag chos dbyings klong du skyabs su mchi //
NK016(ma)017:32: 'gro kun sgrol phyir rdo rje'i sems bskyed do //
NK016(ma)017:36: rdo rje'i sa gzhir ra gur bla re 'khrigs //
NK016(ma)017:37: ye shes me ram kha dog rnam lnga 'bar //
NK016(ma)017:38: phyi rol gser 'khor me 'khor rtsibs stong 'bar //
NK016(ma)017:39: rtsibs steng sprul pa'i pho nya lcags sdig 'gyed //
NK016(ma)017:40: dbus su 'byung bzhi ri rab pad+ma'i steng //
NK016(ma)017:41: sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte ba gzhal yas khang //
NK016(ma)017:42: mtshan nyid yongs rdzogs drag po'i rgyan gyis spras //
NK016(ma)017:43: rtsibs brgyad 'khor lo'i lte bar chos 'byung dbus //
NK016(ma)017:44: rdo rje h+aum yig 'bar ba'i 'phro 'du las //
NK016(ma)017:45: khro rgyal pad+ma drag po he ru ka /
NK016(ma)017:46: me dpung ltar dmar khros 'khrugs rngams pa'i gzugs //
NK016(ma)017:47: phyag g.yas rdo rje rtse dgu nam mkhar 'phyar //
NK016(ma)017:48: phyag g.yon thugs sprul lcags sdig nag po ni //
NK016(ma)017:49: mig dgu bgrad cing kha dgus dgra bgegs za //
NK016(ma)017:50: bco brgyad rwa yis gdon bgegs snying nas 'dzin //
NK016(ma)017:51: yang sprul nying sprul stong gsum 'gengs pa 'dzin //
NK016(ma)017:52: thod skam dbu rgyan mgo rlon do shal 'phyang //
NK016(ma)017:53: zhal gdangs mche gtsigs spyan gsum dmar zlum bgrad //
NK016(ma)017:54: dbu skra sma ra smin ma me bzhin 'bar //
NK016(ma)017:55: dpal gyi chas brgyad gar gyi nyams dgur ldan //
NK016(ma)017:56: pang na yum chen rdo rje mkha' 'gro sngo //
NK016(ma)017:57: gri thod 'dzin pas 'khyud cing gnyis med sbyor //
NK016(ma)017:58: thugs kar phyag na rdo rje mthon mthing mdog /
NK016(ma)017:59: phyag g.yas rdo rje g.yon pas sdigs mdzub mdzad //
NK016(ma)017:60: gser gyi mchod rten bum par sku brten bzhugs //
NK016(ma)017:61: gtso bo'i spyi bor pad+ma sam+b+ha wa //
NK016(ma)017:62: mthing ga rdo rje thod pa kha t+w+aam bsnams //
NK016(ma)017:63: 'dzum zhal mdzes ldan za 'og ber chen gsol //
NK016(ma)017:64: sha 'u'i gnyen zhu rgod ldem rtse sgros brgyan //
NK016(ma)017:65: spyi bo'i gtsug na sprul pa'i mkha' lding ni //
NK016(ma)017:66: spu gri'i me gshog 'bar ba g.yob cing sdeb //
NK016(ma)017:67: phyogs bzhi'i rtsibs la rigs bzhi'i mkha' 'gro ni //
NK016(ma)017:68: dkar ser dmar ljang gri thod kha t+w+aam 'dzin //
NK016(ma)017:69: gar stabs kyis 'gying bde ba'i ro yis gang //
NK016(ma)017:70: mtshams bzhir bcud ldan rin chen bum pas brgyan //
NK016(ma)017:71: shar sgor gsang bdag phyag rdor sngon po ni //
NK016(ma)017:72: rdo rje 'phyar zhing sdigs mdzub drag por bsgreng //
NK016(ma)017:73: lho sgor 'jam dpal gshin rje sku mdog ser //
NK016(ma)017:74: g.yas pa ral gri g.yon pa sdigs mdzub can //
NK016(ma)017:75: nub sgor rta mgrin dmar po rta skad 'tsher //
NK016(ma)017:76: dbyug tho 'phyar zhing sdigs mdzub me chen 'bar //
NK016(ma)017:77: byang sgor yak+sha me dbal mthing nag brjid //
NK016(ma)017:78: tho chen 'phyar zhing lcags kyu me 'bar gdengs //
NK016(ma)017:79: kun kyang rngams brjid dur khrod chas kyis brgyan //
NK016(ma)017:80: ye shes bskal pa'i me dpung sku las 'bar //
NK016(ma)017:81: lha tshogs kun gyi gnas gsum yig 'bru gsum //
NK016(ma)017:82: rdo rje gsum gyi ngo bos mtshan par gyur //
NK016(ma)017:84: snying ga'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas ye shes kyi 'khor lo spyan drangs par bsam la /
NK016(ma)017:86: rnga yab gling dang o rgyan yul //
NK016(ma)017:87: zangs mdog dpal gyi ri bo nas //
NK016(ma)017:90: zhes dang tshig bdun gsol 'debs kyang brjod pa'i mthar /
NK016(ma)017:91: e h+ye hi badz+ra sa ma ya dzah phem phem hrim hrim hrim /
NK016(ma)017:93: dzahh+aum bam hohs dgug gzhug bcing mnyes byas te dam ye dbyer med du bsam mo //
NK016(ma)017:94: hoh rgyal ba rigs lnga'i lha tshogs kyis //
NK016(ma)017:95: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang bskur bas //
NK016(ma)017:96: yon tan kun rdzogs 'od dpag med //
NK016(ma)017:97: 'khor la gtso bos rgyas btab bo //
NK016(ma)017:99: phyi nang gi mchod rdzas rnams byin gyis brlabs te /
NK016(ma)017:100: hoh me tog la sogs phyi mtshod rdzas //
NK016(ma)017:101: 'dod yon lnga po nang gi rdzas //
NK016(ma)017:102: gnyis med 'khril sbyor gsang ba'i rdzas //
NK016(ma)017:103: bdud rtsi lnga po dam tshig rdzas //
NK016(ma)017:104: sha lnga la sogs gtor ma'i rdzas //
NK016(ma)017:105: rtsa brgyad sman sbyor bdud rtsi sman //
NK016(ma)017:107: spros bral ka dag don dam ste //
NK016(ma)017:108: mchod sprin rab 'byams gcig bsdus pas //
NK016(ma)017:109: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs thams cad mchod //
NK016(ma)017:111: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)017:113: ma h+aa ba ling+ta kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)017:115: rgyal ba kun gyi drag po'i sku //
NK016(ma)017:117: thugs rje rmad byung dkyil 'khor gtso //
NK016(ma)017:119: ces pa tsam mam spro na bstod pa gzhan yang bya /
NK016(ma)017:120: thugs ka'i sa bon sngags kyis bskor //
NK016(ma)017:122: bgegs bcom rgyal ba'i byin rlabs bsdus //
NK016(ma)017:123: rigs 'dus rgyal ba'i bdag nyid nga'o //
NK016(ma)017:124: +aahh+aum artsiga nirtsiga na mo b+ha ga wa te h+aum h+aum +aahh+aum h+aum phata phata /
NK016(ma)017:126: a ya ma du ru tsa sha na sa ma ya badz+ra ga ru da h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)017:127: r+aa dza gnod byed kyi snying la m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)017:129: badz+ra d+aa ki ni h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)017:141: gtso bo'i thugs ka'i phyag rdor gyi //
NK016(ma)017:142: thugs srog h+aum yig rab tu 'bar //
NK016(ma)017:143: h+aum gi 'brug sgra cher bsgrags pas //
NK016(ma)017:144: h+aum gi sprin gyis phyogs kun khyab //
NK016(ma)017:145: h+aum h+aum zhes pa h+aum sgrub ste /
NK016(ma)017:146: rim pa bzhin ci nus bzlas pa'i mthar mchod cing bstod nas 'dod don gsol ba gdab bo //
NK016(ma)017:147: tshogs mchod dang mgron gzhan gyi gtor ma bsngo ba sogs byed na skabs 'dir bya zhing /
NK016(ma)017:148: mthar h+aum h+aum zhes rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad 'od gsal du bsdu /
NK016(ma)017:149: phata phata de las thun mtshams kyi lha skur langs nas smon lam shis brjod rnams bya'o //
NK016(ma)017:150: gsum pa dbang gi cho ga ni /
NK016(ma)017:151: dkyil 'khor sgrub mchod bdag mdun dbyer med nyid las /
NK016(ma)017:152: khyad par bum pa la dmigs nas bzlas pa ci
NK016(ma)017:153: rigs pa dang ting nge 'dzin gyis dbang len pa
NK016(ma)017:154: rnams bya'o // slob ma'i bya ba khrus byas /
NK016(ma)017:156: me tog bkye bsdu byas nas /
NK016(ma)017:157: sngon 'gro'i chos bshad ci rigs pa las /
NK016(ma)017:158: khyad par gdul bya zhi bas mi thul ba rnams
NK016(ma)017:159: 'dul phyir bla ma drag po'i sgrub thabs dang las
NK016(ma)017:160: rab 'byams zab 'dril khyad par can mang du gsungs
NK016(ma)017:161: pa las / mchog tu gyur pa'i sgrub thabs 'di
NK016(ma)017:162: nyid o rgyan chen pos 'o bran dpal gyi 'byung
NK016(ma)017:163: pa las / gnas la gnang / de'i sras dpal
NK016(ma)017:164: gyi dbang phyug sogs bdun brgyud zam ma chad par
NK016(ma)017:165: brgyud pa las byung ba'i gdams pa zab mo 'di
NK016(ma)017:166: nyid kyi dbang bskur ba la slob dpon gyi bya
NK016(ma)017:173: dus gsum sangs rgyas 'dus pa'i sku //
NK016(ma)017:174: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa yis //
NK016(ma)017:176: bsgral phyir byin gyis rlob tu gsol //
NK016(ma)017:179: bu khyod su yin ci la dga' /
NK016(ma)017:182: bdag ni bskal bzang snod ldan rigs //
NK016(ma)017:183: lus ngag yid gsum bran du 'bul //
NK016(ma)017:184: gsang sngags bla med dkyil 'khor du //
NK016(ma)017:185: dbang dang byin rlabs stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)017:189: 'jug par rab tu dka' ba yin //
NK016(ma)017:190: dme dang dam 'dor dam nyams dang //
NK016(ma)017:191: pha mas ma gnang ma yin nam //
NK016(ma)017:194: khe dang grags 'dod dam nyams min //
NK016(ma)017:195: rgyal po la sogs ma gnang min //
NK016(ma)017:197: bla ma dam pas bsgral du gsol //
NK016(ma)017:199: skabs 'dir skyabs sems yan lag bdun pa gang 'os shig bya /
NK016(ma)017:200: de nas bla mas lha la gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK016(ma)017:201: hohmi gnas ye shes 'gro ba'i mgon //
NK016(ma)017:202: pad+ma thod phreng dgongs su gsol //
NK016(ma)017:203: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs kyis //
NK016(ma)017:204: slob ma rnams la byin gyis rlobs //
NK016(ma)017:205: zhes gsol ba btab nas yol ba bsal te rdo rje khrid nas nang du bcug /
NK016(ma)017:206: 'di ni dam tshig chu yin te //
NK016(ma)017:207: de ring khyod kyi snying la bstim //
NK016(ma)017:208: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK016(ma)017:209: bka' las ma 'da' dam tshig srungs //
NK016(ma)017:210: sa ma ya i dam na ra kan /
NK016(ma)017:212: de ring phyin chad bu khyod kyi //
NK016(ma)017:213: gsang chen rdo rje 'di yin pas //
NK016(ma)017:214: nga la brnyas par ma byed cig /
NK016(ma)017:215: brnyas na rdo rje'i dmyal bar ltung //
NK016(ma)017:216: zhes rdo rje spyi bor bzhag ste dam la bzhag /
NK016(ma)017:218: bla ma yi dam dbyer med dgongs //
NK016(ma)017:219: byang chub snying po 'dren bgyid cing //
NK016(ma)017:220: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal zlog pa'i thabs //
NK016(ma)017:221: lam mchog bdag la stsol du gsol //
NK016(ma)017:222: lan gsum gyis gsol ba btab /
NK016(ma)017:224: slob ma skad cig gis dbang drag 'bar ba'i skur bskyed /
NK016(ma)017:225: snying gar g.yung drung dmar po g.yon 'khor gyi dbus
NK016(ma)017:226: su rdo rje phag mo dang yan lag bzhi la
NK016(ma)017:227: rigs bzhi'i mkha' 'gro gsal btab g.yon du 'khor bas
NK016(ma)017:228: mkha' 'gro rnams bde ba'i gar byed pa la sems
NK016(ma)017:229: bzung / de las 'od 'phros phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK016(ma)017:230: byang sems thams cad spyan drangs nas dbyer med du
NK016(ma)017:232: rtsa sngags la a be sha btags pa bzla zhing spos dang rol mo'i sgra sbyar /
NK016(ma)017:233: ye shes phebs nas brtan par bya /
NK016(ma)017:234: hoh rin chen rdzas kyi me tog 'di //
NK016(ma)017:236: sngon sbyangs las 'phro gang yod pa'i //
NK016(ma)017:237: yi dam de la 'bab par shog /
NK016(ma)017:238: pra ti gri h+na h+aum zhes dor /
NK016(ma)017:239: rigs dang mthun pa'i ming btags me tog mgo bor bcings te /
NK016(ma)017:240: pra ti sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)017:241: bod+hi tsit+ta push+pe hoh zhes brjod /
NK016(ma)017:242: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa yis //
NK016(ma)017:244: de phyir ma rig ling thog ni //
NK016(ma)017:245: de ring bdag gi bsal bar bgyi //
NK016(ma)017:246: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK016(ma)017:249: da ni dad pa rab tu bskyed //
NK016(ma)017:251: dngos grub thams cad de ring thob //
NK016(ma)017:252: ces dkyil 'khor dang lha'i rnam par bstan /
NK016(ma)017:253: de nas dbang dngos gzhi'i don du /
NK016(ma)017:254: dus gsum rgyal ba 'dus pa'i sku //
NK016(ma)017:255: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa yis //
NK016(ma)017:256: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang mchog rnams //
NK016(ma)017:257: skal ldan bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)017:258: bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum rnams //
NK016(ma)017:259: smin cing grol bar mdzad du gsol //
NK016(ma)017:261: dus gsum bde gshegs thams cad kyi //
NK016(ma)017:262: thugs kyi gsang ba 'di yin pas //
NK016(ma)017:263: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang mchog rnams //
NK016(ma)017:264: skal ldan khyod la sbyin par bya'o //
NK016(ma)017:266: bum pa spyi bor bzhag la /
NK016(ma)017:268: bkra shis rgyas byed bum pa'i pho brang nas //
NK016(ma)017:269: bla ma rigs lnga'i lha tshogs 'od du zhu //
NK016(ma)017:270: skye med byang chub sems kyi bdud rtsi'i chu //
NK016(ma)017:271: spyi bor bzhag pas dbang skur mchog gyur nas //
NK016(ma)017:272: lus ngag yid gsum sgrib pa kun byang ste //
NK016(ma)017:273: bkra shis rnam par rgyal ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK016(ma)017:274: bud+d+ha gu ru a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK016(ma)017:275: h+aum badz+ra s+w+aa rat+na hrihpad+ma h+aa karma gu ru a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aa /
NK016(ma)017:276: zhes dbang bskur zhing bum chu blud /
NK016(ma)017:277: dbang don ngo sprod bum dbang ngo //
NK016(ma)017:278: thod pa mgrin par bzhag la /
NK016(ma)017:280: bkra shes mtshan ldan ye shes ka p+aa la //
NK016(ma)017:281: bdud rtsi 'chi med ye shes lnga yi rdzas //
NK016(ma)017:282: ma bcos bde chen gnyis med byang chub sems //
NK016(ma)017:283: yab yum gnyis med sbyar ba'i bdud rtsi 'dis //
NK016(ma)017:284: skal ldan khyod gyi ngag la dbang bskur bas //
NK016(ma)017:285: bde chen ye shes gsang ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK016(ma)017:288: me long snying gar bzhag la /
NK016(ma)017:290: me long zlum po chos dbyings ye shes ngang //
NK016(ma)017:291: dag cing gsal la dri ma med pa 'di //
NK016(ma)017:292: gsal la ngos bzung med par rang gi sems //
NK016(ma)017:293: sems nyid ka dag ye nas lhun rdzogs don //
NK016(ma)017:294: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes 'di bstan pas //
NK016(ma)017:295: shes rab ye shes dbang dang ldan par shog /
NK016(ma)017:296: gu ru pra dz+ny+aa dz+ny+aa na a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK016(ma)017:299: gu ru'i sku spyi bor gzhag la /
NK016(ma)017:301: chos sku'i ngang las longs spyod rdzogs skur shar //
NK016(ma)017:302: bdud 'dul sprul sku pad+ma 'byung gnas sku //
NK016(ma)017:303: sku yi 'od zer nyi ma sprin bral ltar //
NK016(ma)017:304: gdul bya'i blo yi rmongs 'thibs ma lus 'joms //
NK016(ma)017:305: chos sku'i zhing khams nam mkha'i mtha' mnyam gyis //
NK016(ma)017:306: gdul bya dpag med dbyings su 'dul mdzad pa //
NK016(ma)017:307: chos sku nyi ma 'od zer zhes grags pa //
NK016(ma)017:308: dmigs med mkha' ltar khyab la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK016(ma)017:309: sku yi dbang mchog dus 'dir bskur du gsol //
NK016(ma)017:310: badz+ra gu ru pad+ma thod phreng rtsal k+aa ya a b+hi shany+tsi h+aum /
NK016(ma)017:312: +aah long spyod rdzogs sku mtshan dpe ldan //
NK016(ma)017:313: tshangs dbyangs ka la ping+ka'i sgra //
NK016(ma)017:314: stong gsum mi mjed bye ba brgya'i //
NK016(ma)017:315: dpag med sems can thams can kun //
NK016(ma)017:316: dri med gsung gis rnam gnon pa //
NK016(ma)017:317: seng ge sgra sgrog pad+ma'i gsung //
NK016(ma)017:318: 'gag med gsung gi rdo rjer bstod //
NK016(ma)017:319: gsung gi dbang mchog dus 'dir stsol //
NK016(ma)017:322: mngal skyon ma gos sprul ba'i sku //
NK016(ma)017:323: gling bzhi bye ba phrag brgya ru //
NK016(ma)017:324: sprul pa dpag med so sor 'gyed //
NK016(ma)017:326: mtshan ldan rin chen ltar mi ngoms //
NK016(ma)017:327: sh+aakya seng ge'i sku la bstod //
NK016(ma)017:328: thugs kyi dbang mchog dus 'dir stsol //
NK016(ma)017:330: slar yang spyi bor bzhag la /
NK016(ma)017:332: longs sku gsal rdzogs thod phreng rtsal //
NK016(ma)017:333: sprul sku rdo rje gro lod che //
NK016(ma)017:335: sngon nas khyed dang smon lam gcig /
NK016(ma)017:336: da ltar slob ma'i lhar 'dzin gyis //
NK016(ma)017:337: sku bzhi yongs rdzogs dbang thob shog /
NK016(ma)017:338: zhi drag gi snying po'i mthar /
NK016(ma)017:339: sa ma ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK016(ma)017:340: de dag re re'i mthar sku slob ma la thim /
NK016(ma)017:341: sku gsung thugs dang slob ma'i lus ngag yid gsum dbyer med du gyur par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)017:344: me tog gi phreng ba mgo la bzhag /
NK016(ma)017:346: dbang drag pad+ma thod phreng rtsal //
NK016(ma)017:347: tshe la dbang mdzin 'od dpag med //
NK016(ma)017:348: rin chen me tog dbang bskur bas //
NK016(ma)017:349: tshe yi dbang bskur thob par shog /
NK016(ma)017:350: badz+ra gu ru +aa yur+dz+ny+aa na a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah shar gyi rdo rje mgo bor bzhag ste /
NK016(ma)017:351: thugs sprul gsang bdag rdo rje 'dzin //
NK016(ma)017:352: rdo rje chos kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK016(ma)017:353: nyon mongs nad gdon rnam rtog bcom //
NK016(ma)017:354: thugs mchog ye shes dbang rdzogs shog /
NK016(ma)017:355: badz+ra p+aa ni h+aum a b+hi lho'i bdud rtsi mgor bzhag /
NK016(ma)017:357: gdung sel bdud rtsi'i dbang bskur bas //
NK016(ma)017:358: tshe dpal bsod nams ye shes rgyas //
NK016(ma)017:359: sku mchog lhun grub dbang thob shog /
NK016(ma)017:360: many+dzu sh+r+ai h+aum a b+hi nub kyi dril bu mgor bzhag /
NK016(ma)017:361: gsung sprul rta mgrin rgyal po ste //
NK016(ma)017:362: gsung dbyangs dril bu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK016(ma)017:363: mos pa rnam bzhis dbang bsdus nas //
NK016(ma)017:364: gsung dbyangs rnam dag dbang thob shog /
NK016(ma)017:365: h+ya ya g+r+ai wa h+aum a b+hi byang gi phur pa mgor bzhag /
NK016(ma)017:366: phrin las sprul pa yak+sha me dbal gyis //
NK016(ma)017:367: ye shes rdo rje phur pa'i dbang bskur bas //
NK016(ma)017:368: dgra bgegs 'byung po ma lus tshar bcad nas //
NK016(ma)017:369: phrin las lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK016(ma)017:370: badz+ra kro d+ha yak+sha h+aum a b+hi khyung mgor bzhag /
NK016(ma)017:371: yon tan sprul pa bya khyung rgyal po ste //
NK016(ma)017:372: mkha' lding rdo rje 'jigs byed dbang bskur bas //
NK016(ma)017:373: gdug pa'i sa bdag klu gnyan 'joms pa dang //
NK016(ma)017:374: yon tan lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK016(ma)017:375: ga ru da h+aum a b+hi rdo rje lag g.yas su gtad /
NK016(ma)017:376: rdo rje rtse dgus sa dgu gnon //
NK016(ma)017:377: h+aum dgu ram dgus rab tu brgyan //
NK016(ma)017:378: thod phreng pad+ma rgyal po yis //
NK016(ma)017:379: phyag mtshan 'di ni khyod la sbyin //
NK016(ma)017:381: lcags sdig g.yon du gtad la /
NK016(ma)017:382: thugs sprul lcags sdig nag po ni //
NK016(ma)017:383: mgo dgu kha dgu mig dgu bgrad //
NK016(ma)017:384: rwa chen bco brgyad bgegs la gzengs //
NK016(ma)017:385: thod phreng rdo rje gshog rgod kyi //
NK016(ma)017:386: phyag mtshan 'di ni khyod la sbyin //
NK016(ma)017:387: lha srin sde brgyad dbang du bsdus //
NK016(ma)017:388: kro d+ha yak+sha a b+hi gtor dbang bskur la /
NK016(ma)017:389: bla ma yi dam dbyer med pa'i //
NK016(ma)017:390: dam rdzas gtor mas dbang bskur bas //
NK016(ma)017:391: sku yi byin rlabs lus la zhugs //
NK016(ma)017:392: gsung gi byin rlabs ngag la phob //
NK016(ma)017:393: thugs kyi byin rlabs sems la stsol //
NK016(ma)017:394: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK016(ma)017:396: ba ling+ta k+aa ya wa k+tsit+ta a b+hi shany+tsa h+aum /
NK016(ma)017:397: zhes dbang bskur nas gtor ma'i lha slob ma la bstim nas sems spros bral du bzhag /
NK016(ma)017:398: dam rdzas dngos grub tu sbyin /
NK016(ma)017:399: rjes dam tshig khas blang ba dang man+dala sogs bya zhing /
NK016(ma)017:400: rjes chog mchod bstod bzod gsol gshegs bsdu smon lam shis brjod rnams bya'o //
NK016(ma)017:401: rnam 'gyur khro gtum dmigs med thugs //
NK016(ma)017:402: spros bral rdo rje drag po yis //
NK016(ma)017:403: sgrub thabs bka' ma 'o bran gyi //
NK016(ma)017:404: gdams pa'i rgya mtsho bcud du dril //
NK016(ma)017:405: drag dmar bka' ma 'o bran lugs su grags pa'i sgrub thabs dbang dang bcas pa'i le'u tshan no //
